  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that individuals receiving the brief substance use intervention
      will have better substance use and intimate partner violence outcomes than individuals
      receiving the general health improvement intervention. All participants receive standard
      batterer intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
